32e5aca9a315fb985fafa0b4355e4498c1f877fc1f0b58ad4ac261fb9fbced9f026c7756a5f2af7d61ce756b55c8cd02811bb08df397040e93510056f073756b  0001-gquark-fix-initialization-with-c-constructors.patch"
